getIfaceLinksByEquipmentSpec

protected IfaceLinks getIfaceLinksByEquipmentSpec(IPNet sourceIP,
                                                  java.lang.String EquipmentSpecification)
Returns all the IfaceLink links matching an 'equipment specification' string. The format of the 'equipment specification' string is: equipment-name'|'[iface-name|IPaddress]

Parameters:
EquipmentSpec - Equipment specification used to filter.
Returns:
a ifaceLinks list containing the links.
